---
import ContentLayout from "../layouts/ContentLayout.astro";
---

<ContentLayout
    title="Corporate Scholarship"
    description="Support academic excellence through corporate sponsorship. Partner with Green Schools Foundation to create named scholarships for outstanding students."
    showBreadcrumbs={true}
    breadcrumbs={[
        { name: "Foundation Initiatives", href: "/foundation-initiatives" },
        { name: "Corporate Scholarship", href: "/corporate-scholarship" }
    ]}
>
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Corporate Sponsorship Levels</h2>
        <p>
            Corporate sponsors play a vital role in supporting academic excellence at Green Local Schools. By partnering with Green Schools Foundation, your organization can create named scholarships that directly benefit outstanding students while gaining recognition throughout our community.
        </p>
        <p>
            Corporate sponsors may select to financially support any one or more of the Green Schools Foundation initiatives. Scholarships can be designated for either <strong>academic scholarships</strong> (students pursuing university or college) or <strong>school-to-work scholarships</strong> (students entering a trade or vocational program).
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 mb-12">
        <!-- Member Sponsor -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-gray-100 px-6 py-4 border-b border-gray-200">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">Member Sponsor</h3>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600">$500</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Recognition on the Green Schools Foundation website</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Silver Sponsor -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-gray-200 px-6 py-4 border-b border-gray-300">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">Silver Sponsor</h3>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600">$1,500</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Named $1,500 Scholarship and participation at annual Senior Awards Night</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Company/Organization listed on GSF website, print material and social media platforms</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Gold Sponsor -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-yellow-300 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-yellow-100 px-6 py-4 border-b border-yellow-300">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-yellow-800">Gold Sponsor</h3>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600">$3,000</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Two</strong> Named $1,500 Scholarships and participation at annual Senior Awards Night</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Company/Organization listed on GSF website, print material and social media platforms</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Platinum Sponsor -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-gray-400 overflow-hidden md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-300 to-gray-200 px-6 py-4 border-b border-gray-400">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">Platinum Sponsor</h3>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600">$6,000</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Named $6,000 Scholarship and participation at the annual Senior Awards Night</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <span class="font-semibold">Donor choice:</span>
                            <ul class="mt-1 ml-4 text-sm space-y-1">
                                <li>One $6,000 Scholarship, or</li>
                                <li>A $1,500 Scholarship renewable for up to four years, or</li>
                                <li>Four $1,500 scholarships in the same year</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Company/Organization listed on GSF website, print material and social media platforms</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Legacy Sponsor -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl border-2 border-primary-500 overflow-hidden md:col-span-2">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-500 px-6 py-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Legacy Sponsor (Endowed)</h3>
                <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">$15,000</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Named $1,000 Scholarship <strong>in perpetuity*</strong> and participation at the annual Senior Awards Night</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Company/Organization listed on GSF website, print material and social media platforms</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Automatic sponsor at all GSF major fundraising events</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4 italic">*Based on market conditions</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Current Corporate Sponsors</h2>
        <p class="mb-8">
            We are proud to recognize the following organizations and individuals who have partnered with Green Schools Foundation to support student success.
        </p>

        <!-- Legacy Sponsors -->
        <div class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4 flex items-center">
                <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary-600 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                Legacy Sponsors <span class="font-normal text-gray-500 ml-2">($15,000)</span>
            </h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Green Drug Task Force</p>
                    <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full">Academic</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Pritchard Family</p>
                    <div class="flex gap-2 mt-2">
                        <span class="inline-block px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full">Academic</span>
                        <span class="inline-block px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 rounded-full">Trade</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Loving Hands Preschool</p>
                    <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full">Academic</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Jacob Burch/Natalie Burch-Bowling</p>
                    <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full">Academic</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Neva & Barbara Brenneman Future Educator</p>
                    <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full">Academic</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Brenneman Group Trade Scholarship</p>
                    <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 rounded-full">Trade</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Pauline Franks Memorial Scholarship</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">(Dale & Wendy Brott)</p>
                    <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full">Academic</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Gold Sponsors -->
        <div class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-700 mb-4 flex items-center">
                <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                Gold Sponsors <span class="font-normal text-gray-500 ml-2">($3,000)</span>
            </h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Bernier Financial Services</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">(Paul Bernier)</p>
                    <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 rounded-full">Trade</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Silver Sponsors -->
        <div class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-600 mb-4 flex items-center">
                <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                Silver Sponsors <span class="font-normal text-gray-500 ml-2">($1,500)</span>
            </h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Dr. Bryan Scott</p>
                    <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full">Academic</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Donamarc</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">(Brandon Mantel)</p>
                    <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 rounded-full">Trade</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Cuthbert Family Trade Scholarship</p>
                    <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 rounded-full">Trade</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Brian Hoy Good Neighbor Scholarship</p>
                    <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full">Academic</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Camp Y-Noah</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">(Rocky Wargo)</p>
                    <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full">Academic</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Sol/Harris Day</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">(Andrew Lallathin)</p>
                    <span class="inline-block mt-2 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full">Academic</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">Why Become a Corporate Sponsor?</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Make a Lasting Impact</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                    Your sponsorship directly supports deserving students as they pursue higher education and career training. Named scholarships create a meaningful legacy for your organization.
                </p>

                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Community Recognition</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Sponsors receive prominent recognition at Senior Awards Night, on our website, in print materials, and across our social media platforms.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Tax Benefits</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                    Green Schools Foundation is a 501(c)(3) non-profit organization. Your corporate sponsorship is tax-deductible to the extent allowed by law.
                </p>

                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Flexible Support</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Corporate sponsors may choose to support any one or more of the Green Schools Foundation initiatives, tailoring their contribution to align with their values.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section text-center">
        <h2>Ready to Partner with Us?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            Contact us to learn more about corporate sponsorship opportunities and how your organization can make a difference in the lives of Green Local Schools students.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=Corporate Scholarship Inquiry" class="button-primary mr-4">
            Contact Us
        </a>
        <a href="/scholarships" class="button-secondary">
            Learn About Our Scholarships
        </a>
    </div>
</ContentLayout>
